[Student "S"]
{EAST is strong enough to be thinking about game, depending on how good WEST's hand is. 
So he bids 2NT to get more information.

WEST has the exact hand to say 3NT - a suit headed by AKQ.

Game (and bidding) doesn't get much easier.}

